        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "UNIVERSAL FIT ADAPTER: Will fit all 1/8 Flexible Chuck (3.175mm) for rotary tool, electric grinder, electric power drill including for use with Dremel Rotary Tool",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "COMFORT GRIP PEN TIP: Ergonomic pen design with smooth metal surface makes easy, comfortable carving, sanding and polishing. It can used with polishing kits, drill bits, wire brushes, cut off wheels countersinks, flap wheels, mounted stones, grinding wheels, abrasive bits and more",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "WORKING IN TIGHT SPACES: Ideal for engraving and jewelry making the 43\" Flexible Shaft Rotary Tool simplifies working in cramped spaces and allows the user more freedom while working on DIY projects",
