        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "We've all struggled trying to use screwdrivers around corners, sanding an awkward gap, or making precise cuts on a detailed surface.<br/><br/>This 43\" Flex Shaft Extension allows you to work efficiently in those tight, cramped spaces that continued to defy your best efforts until now. The Flexible Shaft Rotary Tool Extension comes ready to use out of the package with all the pieces needed to make your life easier in order to complete your DIY project.<br/><br/>The 1/8 inch Flexible Chuck, Inner cable for flexible shaft motors is a universal fit for any rotary tool, electric drill or grinder that is a 3.175mm size (1/8th inch). The installation is convenient and simple, all connections are included that are needed.<br/><br/>This flexible extension attachment for 1/8 shank rotary tool fits most rotary tools with the included adapters. It is great for grinding, engraving, carving, and more. You won't want to tackle your next handyman project without having this versatile set around.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
